"1  bunch asparagus (about 1 lb.)","2  heads butterhead lettuce such as Boston or Bibb (see Notes)","3 tablespoons extra-virgin olive oil","5 teaspoons fresh lemon juice","1/2 teaspoon honey","1/2 teaspoon salt","1/4 teaspoon freshly shredded lemon zest","1/4 teaspoon freshly ground black pepper","1/8 teaspoon dry mustard","4 ounces perlini mozzarella (tiny balls; see Notes)","2 tablespoons pine nuts"